data.description: Looking for a home that is in a quiet neighborhood yet is only a couple of miles from the retail hub of Narcoossee and 192?  Your 3 year old home welcomes its new owners.  A covered front porch welcomes you.  Enter into a large foyer and hallway with tile floors in all the living spaces and laminate floors in the bedrooms.  Split plan with guest rooms up front near the laundry room, and the main bedroom in the back.  Kitchen, dining and living space are open, welcoming guests and family members.  Granite counters, white cabinets and stainless steel appliances add to the updated look throughout.  Spend more quiet time in the screened in back porch overlooking the large back yard and field beyond.  Need to swim, there is a community pool at the front of the subdivision.  Come see why this home is your next home.
